{"type":"article_comment","id":35761,"parentType":"article","parentId":5072,"uid":2115,"contents":"且不说这两个电脑体的机刻字,真正的武士刀,铭文都是刻在刀茎上,要拆下刀柄才能看到刀铭。<br>\n<br>\n再从刀刃结构上看,图中这把刀,既不是二战军用指挥刀规定的镐造,也不是古刀上常见的切刃造,而是臆造。<br>\n<br>\n此类“军刀”多见于中国各地古玩市场的大小地摊,摊主开价几百到上千元不等,合理成交价一百到二百元之间。<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.redd.it/eyk8kgv1nqk61.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.redd.it/eyk8kgv1nqk61.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.redd.it/eyk8kgv1nqk61.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.redd.it/3nzh59v1nqk61.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.redd.it/3nzh59v1nqk61.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.redd.it/3nzh59v1nqk61.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2021-03-07","agreeCount":1,"discussionCount":0}